Name: Obsolete
About the game: Obsolete is a game of action/classic platformer/exploration in a very strange world where everything degrades very quickly. Play as a creature coming out of the depths in search of knowledge. Why is everything so dark ? Minimalist 2D graphics in a dark and strange universe. Immersive/original soundtrack made by Virgil Marrel . in a game featuring many secrets! This is an immersive short game (1 hours ~) with a classic gameplay Play it with earphone for a better experience.
